- Restores <u>(12 + {g|Encyclopedia:SkillLoreXenos}Lore (Xenos){/g} / 3)</u> {g|Encyclopedia:HitPoints}wounds{/g}
- Removes {g|Encyclopedia:BleedingEffect}bleeding{/g}, {g|Encyclopedia:BurningEffect}burning{/g}, and {g|Encyclopedia:ToxinEffect}toxin{/g}
- Heals one {g|Encyclopedia:Injury}fresh injury{/g}, or, if none, one old injury upon a successful {g|Encyclopedia:SkillMedicae}Medicae{/g} {g|Encyclopedia:Test}test{/g}
- If the character has the <b>Combat Medicae</b> or <b>Field Medic</b> talents, the amount of restored wounds will be increased by the bonuses provided by these talents.

